  <ThingDef ParentName="HatMakeableBase">
    <defName>VFEV_MooseHeaddress</defName>
    <label>moose headdress</label>
    <description>A very heavy, albeit fragile helmet stitched together from many hides and furs made to represent a hardy moose. This shamanistic headdress is believed to bring great durability and tenacity to it's wearer. Due to the simple design, this helmet does not offer defense or insulation.</description>
